OL,4,Csituation' for retirees at risk of debt
OL,6,FA year on from a new IT system being
OL,7,Finstalled by West Midlands Pension
OL,8,FFund, delays with pension payouts are
OL,9,Fstill ongoing for retirees who have
OL,10,Fdescribed feeling like they are in
OL,11,F"limbo".
OL,13,FThe most recent figures from the
OL,14,FWolverhampton-based organisation,
OL,15,Frevealed in April, suggest 2,896 cases
OL,16,Fare still waiting to be finalised.
