OL,6,FEarlier this year West Midlands
OL,7,FPension Fund (WMPF) said the delays
OL,8,Fwere due to the computer upgrade last
OL,9,FJuly, and they were "making progress
OL,10,Fin recovering service standards."
OL,12,FBut retirees continue to contact ITV
OL,13,FCentral to share their desperation at
OL,14,Fmonths of delays without their money.
OL,16,F"It's not right that people are having
OL,17,Fto wait all this time"
