OL,3,CPension company delays mean 'desperate
OL,4,Csituation' for retirees at risk of debt
OL,6,FHilary Cawley from Coventry is yet to
OL,7,Fsee a penny from her WMPF pension
OL,8,Fsince she retired earlier this year as
OL,9,Fa school technician.
OL,11,FShe triggered her pension last
OL,12,FNovember, organising her paperwork
OL,13,Fbefore Christmas, as she feared
OL,14,Freports of how long it would take.
OL,16,FShe said she's now been told she
OL,17,Fshould receive her money in the next
OL,18,Feight weeks, but said it has been
OL,19,Fmonths of stress.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
