OL,3,CPension company delays mean 'desperate
OL,4,Csituation' for retirees at risk of debt
OL,6,F"It's a bit like being in limbo, you
OL,7,Fwant to look forward to something but
OL,8,Fyou can't", Hilary said. "I worked in
OL,9,Fa school for 29 years and I paid my
OL,10,Fpension for all of that time. It's not
OL,11,Fright that people are having to wait
OL,12,Fall this time."
OL,14,F"I even offered to go to their offices
OL,15,Fand sit in their office with them and
OL,16,Fhelp them fill out the forms and maybe
OL,17,Fthey could go a bit quicker."
OL,19,FShe is not alone in her experience.
OL,20,FOthers, who wish to be anonymous, have
OL,21,Ftold us of their struggles.
