OL,6,FOne person said "I am relying on this
OL,7,Fmoney and am getting further and
OL,8,Ffurther into debt."
OL,10,F"They've been dismissive of the
OL,11,Fsituation and its impact on us" said
OL,12,Fanother.
OL,14,FAnother said "My partner is now
OL,15,Fsuffering stress. We call and get
OL,16,Ffobbed off with different excuses."
OL,18,FAndy Bright from Smethwick in
OL,19,FBirmingham has sent over sixty emails
OL,20,Fand numerous calls to WMPF.
