OL,6,FHis paperwork was sent to their
OL,7,Foffices last August.
OL,9,FAndy took ill health retirement from
OL,10,Fhis council job in 2022, after
OL,11,Frecovery from a double lung transplant
OL,12,Fmade it difficult to go back to his
OL,13,Fjob.
OL,15,FHe has part-time work with a charity
OL,16,Fto help pay the bills, and said his
OL,17,Fhealth concerns have made the
OL,18,Fsituation feel desperate. He said"
