OL,6,F"I want to enjoy it whilst I'm still
OL,7,Fhere because the average life
OL,8,Fexpectancy of a lung transplant
OL,9,Frecipient is seven years. I'm six
OL,10,Fyears in now, so I want to be able to
OL,11,Fenjoy what time I have left with my
OL,12,Fwife, my children and my seven
OL,13,Fgrandchildren."
OL,15,FAndy has been told he should have news
OL,16,Fin the next four weeks but he's
OL,17,Fconcerned for others still waiting.
