OL,6,FHe said "In this day and age with all
OL,7,Fthe technology we have there should be
OL,8,Fclearer lines of communication, there
OL,9,Fshould be faster response.
OL,11,F"I just hope that over the next 12
OL,12,Fmonths that they continue to improve
OL,13,Fit and make it better for people who
OL,14,Fare trying to retire."
