OL,6,F"We have sought clarification of the
OL,7,Fcases cited and will investigate
OL,8,Findividual concerns. We are committed
OL,9,Fto continuing to recover our service
OL,10,Flevels and enhance our member
OL,11,Fexperience.
OL,13,F"We continue to increase access and
OL,14,Fcapacity to serve all our members.
OL,15,FCustomers receive general updates
OL,16,Fthrough our website and direct to
OL,17,Ftheir inbox, with further updates
OL,18,Fprovided in response to individual
OL,19,Frequests.
