OL,6,F"Our customer servicing centre has now
OL,7,Ffully reopened and we are providing
OL,8,Fface-to-face support to members across
OL,9,Fthe region.
OL,11,F"Online services are enabling more
OL,12,Fmembers to plan for their retirement
OL,13,Fand we are reducing the time taken to
OL,14,Fmake payments to members, with
OL,15,Fsupplementary payrolls continuing to
OL,16,Frun twice weekly."
